data.description: Be the first to see Lehigh's best value! This 3/2 + den charming home is in a desirable location. New roof! Close to SR 82 for easy access to airport, shopping, and I-75. New flooring, kitchen appliances, solar hot water heater, and well system. Relax outside on the front porch or in the screened patio with the beautiful view of the water. Huge open kitchen with lights under cabinets, new appliances, and plenty of cabinet space. The interior boasts an open-concept design, seamlessly connecting the living, dining, and kitchen areas. Perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quality family time. Ensured safety with security cameras. Solar panels. Primary is a true retreat, offering a peaceful haven with a spacious layout, a walk-in closet, and bath offers dual sinks with a separate tub and shower.  Garage with enough room for 2 cars and some workspace! Lot to east of property is also optional to purchase. Everything you need is at your disposal in this quiet and central location! I wouldn't wait! Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and comfort that 1237 Edgewood St E has to offer!
